Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.46,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,FAMOUS DETECTIVE HOLMES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:41.01,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,The Evil Genius, Professor Moriarty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:42.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:14.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:18.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The crown of Mazalin?!\NThis is going to be a very rare catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:21.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The Banker Sampton's mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:35.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, his mansion is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:36.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:04.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling, this is very enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:06.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm having a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:28.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sampton, I'm sorry to call on\Nyou in the middle of your party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:30.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a very\Nimportant business meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:31.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:33.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The pleasure was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:35.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:37.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is very strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sampton?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:45.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:49.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, the crown of Mazalin is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:51.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the crown of Mazalin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:56.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:58.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The crown of Mazalin\Nhas disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:01.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be a\Nbig scandal, Mr. Sampton.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:07.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The crown of Mazalin\Nis a national treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:09.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I... Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If it has been stolen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sampton,\Nwho has access to this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:16.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:19.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! My son also knows\Nwhere I keep the spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The spare key?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:22.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:26.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It was gone when I came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:30.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But if only two people\Ncould access this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:32.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be. My son wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:34.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to think so... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:37.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard so many rumours about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:38.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:41.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we should\Ncall the police now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:43.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:44.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:51.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:07.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all a bunch of imbeciles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They would never be\Nable to figure out my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:16.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Inspector Lestrade\Nof Scotland Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:18.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:21.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the inspector?\NI was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:23.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,As I asked you before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:25.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,you didn't allow anyone\Nto leave the house, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help find the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:30.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I can take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:34.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can solve even the most\Ndifficult cases instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:37.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we already on Baker Street?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the street where\NSherlock Holmes lives, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He has his own detective office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You really never heard of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:58.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:01.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very unusual,\Nyou not knowing Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:03.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:10.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He can solve even the most\Ndifficult cases quite easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't happened on\Nany difficult cases, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:14.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:18.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to live with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:19.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:25.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Baker Street. 221 B. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:27.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We've finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:31.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:37.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:52.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I arrived so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:07:00.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm Watson. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to\Ncome here tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:04.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But I arrived late tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:08.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:12.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:15.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:20.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a very nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:27.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:32.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:33.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:41.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the room.\NPlease follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:44.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:55.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:59.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. You are very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a lovely room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:10.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:13.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I like it. Very quiet too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:19.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There are flowers in the garden.\NBesides, a beautiful lady like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:22.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:26.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I think beauty is peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:28.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where is Mr. Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:32.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He is already sleeping.\NPlease meet him tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:33.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.96,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,This is completely ruining the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:40.33,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they would let us go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:09:00.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, they didn't touch\Nanything but the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who was\Nin this safe room was?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:06.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only Mr. Zeal,\Nthe son of Mr. Sampton.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:13.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:29.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the only door\Nto enter the safe room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:33.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This was definitely an inside job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And, there are only two people\Nwho can enter this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:42.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Zeal has a fiancée\Nwho Mr. Sampton hates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:44.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:48.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps this was his last resort since\NMr. Sampton was against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:03.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say hello to the client\Nwho requested this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:05.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Mr. Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:11.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This house has so\Nmany beautiful women.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:15.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to tell you when you've just\Nwoken up, but I must go out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:18.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of case is it?\NLet me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:21.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Shields' fiancée\Nis being accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she is Ms. Shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:26.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He is my best friend, Mr. Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mr. Holmes' friend, Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:29.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's hurry.\NDon't mind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:32.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:42.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never believe that Zeal stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:45.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But according to the witnesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:49.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it wasn't a good idea to leave\Nthe house without telling anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:52.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you don't\Ncare if he gets caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:56.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Holmes.\NPlease clear Zeal of suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:04.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The most important question is,\Nwhere is the missing crown now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Those insects of Scotland Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll never find it no matter\Nhow much they search.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:13.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they'll have to start\Nreleasing the guests soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:15.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:20.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Who is that young jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find the crown anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:24.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:26.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't find it in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:28.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The scoundrel must have\Ntaken it with him when he escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:29.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:30.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Holmes is telling us to let him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Holmes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:34.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he trying to stick his\Nnose into my investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:36.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,just because he's been\Ngetting popular recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:38.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lestrade,\NI have no intention of disturbing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:45.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go anywhere if I receive\Na request to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A request to investigate?\NWho hired you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:51.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That is confidential.\NI can't tell you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:52.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Confidential?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:55.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean Zeal,\Nthe one who ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:12:00.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Did I hit the mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:03.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You guessed completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:12.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It would take a good plan\Nto get this crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This was not a job anyone could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, the spare key was\Nin the same place as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm sure it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:31.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, a mark\Nwhere the door was forced.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:35.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Your son said he became suspicious\Nwhen he saw that the door was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:36.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:39.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we can deduce that the suspect...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:41.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't have escaped\Nthrough this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something, Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:54.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Footprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:57.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And this hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to escape from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:06.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's not necessarily true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:07.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:08.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The scratch mark of a hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:10.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A hook?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:13.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,When Zeal and Mr. Sampton\Nentered the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:18.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,the suspect was hiding\Nbehind the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:19.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:23.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But he couldn't use the door,\Nnow that the crown was found missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he quickly escaped\Nfrom the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:29.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They came this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:30.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:33.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,New footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:35.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy, or you'll\Nget hurt Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:37.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:40.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I barely managed to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:42.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they could escape\Ngoing along the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's not true, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I found the rope the\Nsuspect used to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:49.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And the hook that made\Nthe scratch on the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:52.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the suspect is!\NSomebody in the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:53.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:55.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the guests are released...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:58.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,the suspect will come back\Nto pick up the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:13:59.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to wait for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:22.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch, this was too tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:24.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't do things\Nwe're not used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:27.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like we've done\Na good job up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:30.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be a better\Nway to make a living than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:33.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We were better off as pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:37.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain.\NJust prepare for our next task.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:42.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they barely\Nmanaged up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:46.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure Zeal is not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:48.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be equally guilty\Nif you're hiding him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:51.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If you doubt me,\Nwhy don't you check inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:54.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's up to me to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:57.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:00.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to let me know\Nif Zeal tries to contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:03.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll know if you're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:20.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:24.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,She's hiding something.\NWe'll keep watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:32.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any sign of movement?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:38.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait! Don't go just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:40.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Inspector Lestrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you told me you\Nwouldn't disturb my investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a pretty good idea\Nwhere the crown is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:49.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to wait for the suspect\Nto come back to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:52.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,W... What did you say?!\NAre you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:58.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to help me with this.\NIs that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:03.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Our purpose is to investigate\Nand solve the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:07.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate that Inspector Lestrade.\NBut I'll need to talk to her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:09.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:13.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,After I finish talking to her,\Nplease follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:17.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:32.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do\Nyou want me to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:35.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Mr. Holmes is not tricking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:42.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, is he really coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:47.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:51.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How goes it Watson?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:03.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:11.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:15.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:22.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The Professor will be\Nvery proud of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:26.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the crown of Mazalin!\NStart your engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! They're from Scotland Yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn on the engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:38.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:41.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and turn on the engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going Holmes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:48.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll beat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:48.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:54.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Give the crown back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:55.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:57.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:01.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose them! Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Try and get us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:08.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:10.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't treat me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:13.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:14.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:17.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Use all the coal you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,B... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:19.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:21.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:22.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to attack immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:28.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep going,\Neven through fire or water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:32.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the experts on water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat sailors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:39.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! Hard to port!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:39.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay in pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take care of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:51.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost there! After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good! Go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:54.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the maximum speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:59.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good going!\NNow, we will catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stoke more coals!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:08.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hesitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspects are extremely close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:11.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:14.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:16.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:17.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:18.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the helm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:19.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:20.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:29.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:30.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:31.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:34.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody! Start bailing water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:38.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,After you've bailed the water,\Ngo after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hesitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:41.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well! Good bye!\NGood bye! Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about time\Nyou returned the crown?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:48.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't,\NI will have to force you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I shouldn't\Nhave relied on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:05.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, the chivalry of my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.09,0:20:08.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a sailor and I won't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:08.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But chivalrous spirit\Nwill never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:13.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:15.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never let you have the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:17.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take and keep it\Nwith great care!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:18.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:21.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss finally showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:21.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:31.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I don't wanna get wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:34.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We will drown like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailors will never die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:39.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:42.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:48.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:51.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:02.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We're here to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:03.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:04.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:07.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Lestrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, I'll return\Nthe crown with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:15.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:17.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you give up now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:18.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh drat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:19.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It will fall apart if\Nwe push it any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:28.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Full throttle! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:35.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase them! Don't let them beat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:36.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:41.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Don't lose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:42.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Chase!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:43.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:46.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase! Chase! Full throttle! Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:55.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad, Mr. Zeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:56.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Ms. Shields\Nhadn't acted bravely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:02.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,things would have\Nturned out differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:05.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know she\Nwas such a great person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:08.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong to separate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:11.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:12.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:20.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't forget about the brave\Nperson who helped the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:24.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch, that hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:27.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody must be\Ntalking about me again.
