Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:02.68,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lestrade is in a big jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.22,0:24:06.19,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the work of\NProfessor Moriarty.
